                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900915-41-off217 t17900915-41-cd218"></join> last, four pair of silk stockings, value 34 s. and one silk stocking, value 4 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900915-41-victim458" type="victimName">
