                     <interp inst="t17900915-41-person465" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             for payment.</p>
               <p>Whose shop is this? - Mr. 
               <persName id="t17900915-41-person466">
                  Thomas
                   Burgher
               <interp inst="t17900915-41-person466" type="surname" value="Burgher"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-41-person466" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-41-person466" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's shop.</p>
               <p>Mr. Knowlys. Has there been any assignment of the lease from 
               <persName id="t17900915-41-person467">
                  Thomas
                   Burgher
               <interp inst="t17900915-41-person467" type="surname" value="Burgher"></interp>
